Transcription.Text: To all who have shown their practical sympathy and understanding of our task, we offer our grateful thanks. Chapter five. Treatment of boys. 1. General. - 2. The open borstal at Huntercombe is being adapted for use as a medium security borstal, and the adaption of Aylesbury prison as an establishment for young offenders has made further progress.
